  "sattvānurūpā sarvasya śraddhā bhavati bhārata śraddhāmayo'yam puruso yo yacchraddhah sa eva sah",
  "Yajante sattvika devan yaksharakshamsi rajasah pretan bhuta-ganams chaanye yajante tamasa janah",
  "Ashastravihitam ghoram tapyante ye tapo janah, dambhahankarasamyuktah kamaragabalanvitah.",
  "karsayantah śarīrastham bhūtagrāmam acetasah mām caivāntah śarīrastham tān viddhy āsura niścayān",
  "āhārastvapi sarvasya trividho bhavati priyah, yajñastapastathā dānam tesām bhedamimam śrnu ",
